If the NVIDIA card is not used for displaying, or on a Wayland environment,
add @code{nvidia_drm.modeset=1} to @code{kernel-arguments} as well.")
    (license
     (license:nonfree
      (format #f "file:///share/doc/nvidia-driver-~a/LICENSE" version)))))

